title: SANOXY 7" Tablet Stand with USB Keyboard - Black Faux Leather Carrying Case
description:
Please note : it does NOT work for Coby Koros & Kindle fire, blackberry
This black leather case with laptop-style keyboard is the perfect accessory for 7" tablets. This protective cover is multi-functional and lets you type just as you would with your laptop/netbook. This case is equipped with a full working keyboard, a stylus, pockets to hold up to 2 styluses, USB cable, and an extendable stand. Just plug the USB 2.0 cable, attached to the keyboard, right into your tablet and you're all set! Product Dimensions: 9.0 x 5.75 x 1.0 inches. Recommended for use with 7" tablet dimensions up to: 8.75 x 5.5 x 0.75 inches. ** Please make sure to measure the dimensions of your 7" Tablet for a proper fit! **
